('b28b2467-c950-56cb-aea5-d9acfd37118b', '9490faa0-af9d-4259-9aa2-a4b18dc0f023', 'Can I ___ you for some help with my homework?', '我可以請你幫我做功課嗎？', 'ask', 'give', 'take', 'make', 'ask 為動詞，ask for something 表示「要求某物」。', 'ask → 想要得到幫助，就要去 ask。', '2026-07-06 14:55:46', '2026-07-06 14:55:46'),
